{"tid":1674364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貨車司機認連儂牆傷人判社服","createTime":"2019-10-25T07:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T10:20:51.000Z","uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ec673fdd5bf0c2ccf4e82b56d5f4ef425d77d410","tid":1674364,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"貨車司機認連儂牆傷人判社服<br />\n<br />\n2019/10/25 14:32 Cable News<br />\n<br />\n一名貨車司機在連儂牆打傷一名男子，在屯門裁判法院被判一百小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n五十四歲被告司徒文輝，承認襲擊致構成身體傷害罪，他於八月四日晚在輕鐵澤豐站附近撕毀連儂牆海報，被一名男子用手機拍攝，事主被推向牆身、後腦受傷，被告表示是一時衝動犯案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指，法庭不能接受暴力行為，理解被告對社會運動有意見，被人用手機拍攝可能充滿挑釁性，告誡被告要照顧家庭，沒有本錢去衝動。"},{"pid":"7fb7be776c4030c01ba30f22f20889adb732eba0","tid":1674364,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:22:00.000Z","msg":"都係自衞反擊打7佢好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193fb9c9de32463c1a7333720c20d556bb2e006f","tid":1674364,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"再輕啲丫笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6695775eba2409079e41abdb359cb1b46c439ea9","tid":1674364,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"193fb9c9de32463c1a7333720c20d556bb2e006f","tid":1674364,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"再輕啲丫笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:24:34.000Z","msg":"我地打人就傷人19 17㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89dee380e9b7ca0da2ff483a55296e3c7e9b4856","tid":1674364,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母罰千五蚊吖笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3d44e2d552973ff62ad5509ded7deac73b564a","tid":1674364,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19